Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道NERGAL賠償了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給各位相關人士添了許多麻煩後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子總算脫離地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有愛情 有熱血 有友情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是太熱血了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田先生 您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:58.20,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(352,315)\fad(800,350)}在蔚藍的宇宙{\be1\fnsimhei}『{\r\be1}心跳不已{\be1\fnsimhei}』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼爆焰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 丈!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈 你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈...你醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 奈奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來海邊是去不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...我想現在可以安慰他的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了身為情人的我沒別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個光看設計圖就令人興奮不已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有三個新駕駛員要來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不關我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是這次送來的零C戰模組
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒透了 這玩意兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個先不談...明人他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新來的啊 最好是令人討厭的臭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討人厭的傢伙比較好 因為是隨時會陣亡的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是艦長命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 馬上就到達殖民地五月綠二號了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立刻回到艦橋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門開著啊 真是不小心哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要送到地球的山田先生的行李 就是這個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠著海燕丈的犧牲 擊退了麥瑟克將軍的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是損失了駕駛員自己也負傷的激鋼人3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有辦法再次復甦嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一分鐘就可以看到殖民地了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元歪曲防壁解除 準備停泊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是機動戰艦 撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月綠二號 聽得到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是五月綠二號 收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇...好可愛的聲音哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始停泊 準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK  請放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<五月綠二號到再視界還有八秒> <主螢幕>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地方向傳來衝擊波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認受害狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方是五月綠二號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防壁發動機第二區間附近中度破損
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到剛才...還正在通訊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到剛才...還在說話的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 注意有沒有生還者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上檢查發動機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續確認周圍的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候萬一遭到敵人的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看 得慎重點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各員進入艦內警備狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急通告所有成員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不明人物侵入本艦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員確認識別碼的發信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦內補修班繼續作業
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他成員堅守崗位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 麥瑟克將軍這混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢這樣對我的激鋼人3...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 出現了為處於劣勢的我們助陣的好夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是龍崎鐵也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有新的生力軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激剛人V
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從側面確認機影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機有四架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防壁能用嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動機還要花十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五分鐘 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擴大機影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼氣旋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍 最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 丈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意我 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼爆焰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 你怎麼了 丈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈 你振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 奈奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來海邊是去不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈 你太過份了 丈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈子小姐 不 奈奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去海邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...你沒事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的激鋼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你看看我機械軍團的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於海燕丈的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免了麥瑟克將軍的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 損失了駕駛員自己也負傷的激鋼人3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是丈最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最近才知道「激鋼人3」的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越看越著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我好想要拿出舊本事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出同人志參加COSMIKE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<COSMIKE>:也就是俗稱的宇宙同人志即售會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對...妳到底是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會突然掉下來?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是 失敬失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你不會吐一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「現在哪裡還有說失敬」之類的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是Aestivalis零C戰模組
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我方的人應該會傳來識別訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道被挾持了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 只是忘記了識別密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼有自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼索上綁白色的記號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拖吊的基本常識 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是指汽車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果木星蜥蜴會耍這種寶就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了 搞什麼鬼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我要先洗澡 然後吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問...妳叫什麼名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問別人之前得先自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是御統百合香 是本艦的艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是昴涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零C戰模組只有四架?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機庫的殘骸中還剩下一架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒辦法全部帶出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外兩位駕駛員怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 可能還活著也可能掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是駕駛員天野光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇夫座B型 l8歲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的東西是比薩邊邊的硬皮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有稍微受潮的煎餅 請大家多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不好玩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不會...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩個人生還也算不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便把人宰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還活著啊 現在在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前打開工具箱看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣真新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳別關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是鯖魚罐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也是駕駛員 叫真木泉 以下省略
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Aestivalis的檢查補給之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託確認殖民地內的生還者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有回收剩下的一架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 真是條壓搾勞力的船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我要進入戰艦的時候有撞壞了一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:12:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我把牆壁修補過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒狀態解除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 不是聽說還有兩個駕駛員在這裡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有騙人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我本來是個廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 因為你怎麼看都不像駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯...我是廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當駕駛員也是臨時的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始停泊 準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OKOK...請放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:12:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都不把別人的死當成一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連他死了也只有我一個人在難過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是我 有人死的話也會很傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有小惠妳會這麼想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我想以一個駕駛員的身份努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也是漠不關心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是為那傢伙和大家一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有這種心情了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我自己一個人掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己一個人痛苦 一個人不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並不是一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都會有想撒嬌的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦...原來我只是在撒嬌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著以駕駛員的身份加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不快點閃開的話會被踩扁的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力彈射器準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我這就上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我們的好消息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力波充電
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴機去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該在我的鼓勵下讓你一起出擊才對的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起對不起 可是可是不要怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怪就怪那捉弄人的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又有一架出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 白癡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會開宇宙用的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟陸戰用的駕駛艙沒什麼兩樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本是一樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞭解這些基本嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可也是個駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 快迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡要亂搞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有生物反應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的點的位置確認
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅燒豬肉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<音同確認>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要衝進去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為來自撫子的能源傳送要切斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<補助電池所剩時間>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備用電池啟動確認
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始潛行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅燒豬肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到大珍珠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來可以開始回收作業了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的 沒油啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和撫子之間有障礙物的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就沒辦法接收能源啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事是基本中的基本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那我該怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大意的話可是會撞上撫子的力場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔Aestivalis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電腦被蜥蜴侵入了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我浪費能源
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總重量可是對方比較重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用速度的差距衝到它懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近戰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 太快了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外型這麼笨重還如此俐落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是找上門來的架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要打
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天保佑 老天保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙重攻擊...才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你中門大開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 他朝撫子的方向去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡只有廚師一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河 打敗他\N我跟以前的我已不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個撒嬌的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是天河明人V
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子也會有危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱 我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼爆焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人 太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭禧你 明人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 明人你很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦 我在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢 一定是在作夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一個可怕的惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然非常有現實感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這只會是惡夢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是夢!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香奔跑著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像命中注定一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人煩惱著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著戰鬥的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純哭泣著為了他那異常的純情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 琉璃嘀咕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化為宇宙的巴士底獄的撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在點起了革命的烽火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰國魔神豪將軍的首籐剛志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信滿滿地創造機械人動畫的新世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 機動戰艦撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小琉璃的『航海日誌』
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起看哦
